## ğŸ”§ UpdatePost.jsx

### ğŸ“Œ Description:
Allows editing a blog post selected by its ID.

### âœ… APIs Used:
1. Fetch existing data:
```http
GET /posts/{id}
```

2. Submit updated post:
```http
